commands.command_help:
I am MeetX, a bot that will help you find friends, acquaintances, and possibly more. I provide the ability to search for suitable people through profiles, so feel free to create your own and find"brothers in mind" ;)

If you have any questions:
@wwwhatisthiss - developer account
@meetx_discussion - group where you can get help, suggest ideas for improvement or just chat. To improve the quality of the bot, all messages are logged. More information can be found here: https://t.me/meetx_discussion/1
